high_descs: Go forward, then turn left, then turn right to face the table.
Take the tomato from the table, next to the coffee maker.
Go forward, then turn right, to view the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the tomato on the counter, to the left of the sink.
Go to the sink in front of you.
Take the tomato from the sink.
Turn around then turn right to view the counter, to the left of the sink.
Place the tomato on the counter, behind the other tomato.

Take the tomato from the table
Turn right, go forward, turn right at the counter, go forward, turn right at the counter
Put the tomato on the counter

Pick up the tomato in the sink

Pick up a tomato from the table.

Place the tomato on the counter to the left of the sink.

Pick up the tomato from the sink.

Pick up the tomato that is on the table to the left of the coffee machine.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn right and walk over to the section of counter to the left of the sink.
Put the tomato on the front edge of the counter to the left of the sink.
Walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Pick up the tomato that is in the sink basin.
Turn left and begin walking forward, then turn around to face the sink.
Place the tomato on the front edge of the counter to the right of the sink.
